{"type":"message","id":"ec872184","parentId":"d5c0b598","timestamp":"2026-03-25T23:00:00.543Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:8ecc8a2f-8c0c-47da-b813-78ecc92e2cd5 每日新闻与市场早报] 执行每日新闻与市场早报任务：\n0. 查询西安今日天气，生成天气简报，重点给出穿衣建议，提醒是否需要带伞\n\n1. 伊朗-美国战争最新消息：搜索\"伊朗 美国 战争 最新消息\"、\"霍尔木兹海峡\"、\"伊朗战争 全球经济\"，输出10条重要新闻摘要\n\n2. 半导体行业新闻：搜索\"半导体行业新闻\"、\"WiFi芯片\"、\"芯片验证\"、\"ESP32\"、\"乐鑫\"，输出10条行业新闻摘要\n\n3. 乐鑫科技(688018)股票分析：获取最新股价、涨跌幅、成交量，搜索公司公告、研报、最新消息，给出持有/卖出的建议\n\n4. 国内新闻TOP10：搜索\"国内新闻\"、\"中国新闻\"，筛选最重要的10条新闻\n\n5. 国际新闻TOP10：搜索\"国际新闻\"、\"世界新闻\"、\"global news\"，筛选最重要的10条新闻\n\n6. 股票推荐TOP10：搜索\"股票推荐\"、\"买入评级\"、\"券商推荐股票\"，推荐10个值得关注的股票及理由\n\n7. 基金推荐TOP10：搜索\"基金推荐\"、\"优质基金\"、\"基金排行\"，推荐10个值得买入的基金及理由\n\n输出要求：\n- 使用飞书卡片格式\n- 同时将所有信息整理成一个飞书文档，将飞书文档链接附在飞书卡片最后\n- 每个部分用清晰标题分隔\n- 重要信息加粗\n- 股票/基金推荐包含代码/名称+推荐理由\n- 每条新闻/信息必须附上来源和链接，格式：📰 [新闻标题] - [一句话摘要]\\n🔗 来源：[网站名称] | [链接]\n- 如果某条信息无法找到确切来源，标注\"来源待确认\"\n\n完成后通过飞书发送给主人 ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e。\nCurrent time: Thursday, March 26th, 2026 — 07:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-25 23:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774479600539}}
{"type":"message","id":"d29da0e9","parentId":"ec872184","timestamp":"2026-03-25T23:00:11.007Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户现在需要执行每日新闻与市场早报的任务，首先我得一步步来对吧，首先第一步是查西安今天的天气，然后是各个搜索任务，最后整理成飞书文档，再发卡片。首先我应该先调用weather相关的工具？不对，看技能里有weather技能，先读那个skill？或者直接先搜索西安天气？不对，先看weather技能的位置，是~/AppData/Roaming/npm/node_modules/openclaw/skills/weather/SKILL.md，先读这个对吧？然后接下来要做多个web搜索，比如伊朗美国战争的，半导体的，乐鑫股票的，国内国际新闻，股票基金推荐，然后整理成Markdown，然后用feishu_doc创建文档，再用message发送飞书卡片给指定的用户ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e。首先第一步先读weather技能，看看怎么获取西安天气。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_76n41pd238znoatie0ezuqww","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/AppData/Roaming/npm/node_modules/openclaw/skills/weather/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":19919,"output":487,"cacheRead":3896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24302,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774479600546,"responseId":"02177447960191264d8a6219dbbdb6281842e0590025e921a0ec0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"eb295edc","parentId":"d29da0e9","timestamp":"2026-03-25T23:00:11.020Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_76n41pd238znoatie0ezuqww","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: weather\ndescription: \"Get current weather and forecasts via wttr.in or Open-Meteo. Use when: user asks about weather, temperature, or forecasts for any location. NOT for: historical weather data, severe weather alerts, or detailed meteorological analysis. No API key needed.\"\nhomepage: https://wttr.in/:help\nmetadata: { \"openclaw\": { \"emoji\": \"☔\", \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"curl\"] } } }\n---\n\n# Weather Skill\n\nGet current weather conditions and forecasts.\n\n## When to Use\n\n✅ **USE this skill when:**\n\n- \"What's the weather?\"\n- \"Will it rain today/tomorrow?\"\n- \"Temperature in [city]\"\n- \"Weather forecast for the week\"\n- Travel planning weather checks\n\n## When NOT to Use\n\n❌ **DON'T use this skill when:**\n\n- Historical weather data → use weather archives/APIs\n- Climate analysis or trends → use specialized data sources\n- Hyper-local microclimate data → use local sensors\n- Severe weather alerts → check official NWS sources\n- Aviation/marine weather → use specialized services (METAR, etc.)\n\n## Location\n\nAlways include a city, region, or airport code in weather queries.\n\n## Commands\n\n### Current Weather\n\n```bash\n# One-line summary\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=3\"\n\n# Detailed current conditions\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?0\"\n\n# Specific city\ncurl \"wttr.in/New+York?format=3\"\n```\n\n### Forecasts\n\n```bash\n# 3-day forecast\ncurl \"wttr.in/London\"\n\n# Week forecast\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=v2\"\n\n# Specific day (0=today, 1=tomorrow, 2=day after)\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?1\"\n```\n\n### Format Options\n\n```bash\n# One-liner\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%t+%w\"\n\n# JSON output\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=j1\"\n\n# PNG image\ncurl \"wttr.in/London.png\"\n```\n\n### Format Codes\n\n- `%c` — Weather condition emoji\n- `%t` — Temperature\n- `%f` — \"Feels like\"\n- `%w` — Wind\n- `%h` — Humidity\n- `%p` — Precipitation\n- `%l` — Location\n\n## Quick Responses\n\n**\"What's the weather?\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl -s \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%t+(feels+like+%f),+%w+wind,+%h+humidity\"\n```\n\n**\"Will it rain?\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl -s \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%p\"\n```\n\n**\"Weekend forecast\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=v2\"\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- No API key needed (uses wttr.in)\n- Rate limited; don't spam requests\n- Works for most global cities\n- Supports airport codes: `curl wttr.in/ORD`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774479611019}}
